{"tid":415446,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(HX) 香港航空空中服務員 私運黃金赴日被捕","createTime":"2017-09-27T03:39:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T11:16:29.000Z","uid":6604,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e744f1c50b2d9a78314e1916f13ca22a71e28c21","tid":415446,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T03:39:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170927/57259830\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170927%2F57259830&d=2fBAtmxPq8sHyRpGMi7BM04boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=1fab83f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170927%2F57259830&h=61be629b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170927/57259830</a><br />\n<br />\n港航空中服務員化身港版「巴利薛爾」走私違禁品被捕。一名隸屬香港航空的機艙服務員，昨日早上乘搭航班由香港出發往東京成田機場，抵埗清關時被搜出私藏金條，當場被捕。港航證實有員工懷疑攜帶違禁品入境日本，正配合當地海關調查。<br />\n<br />\n香港航空發言人回應，獲悉有機艙服務員懷疑攜帶違禁品入境日本，公司正協助當地海關的調查工作，由於事件正交由海關處理，目前未能提供進一步資料。<br />\n涉事航班為香港航空航班HX606，昨日凌晨2時20分由香港機場起飛，至清晨早上7時40分抵達東京成田機場。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，一名空中服務員接受日本成田機場稅關檢查時，搜出藏有一批未完稅黃金，以未有申報為由遭扣留當地調查，追查涉案人如何避過香港清關檢查，成功將黃金偷運上機。<br />\n<br />\n根據日本法例，走私黃金是一項涉及逃稅的嚴重罪行，輕則罰款，重則包括緩刑執行、等待判決及收監，最高可判罰囚禁5年及罰款500萬日元(折合約35萬港元)，不過由於港日兩地黃金差價為每公斤逾3萬元，有不法分子招攬巿民投身運金行業，甚至組織「運金團」走私黃金入境當地。<br />\n<br />\n日本海關今年7月揭發日本香草航空一班由台灣桃園機場飛抵大阪關西機場的客機，在兩個洗手間牆內發現內藏逾30公斤懷疑走私黃金，懷疑有走私客利用廉航客機飛畢國際線後，轉往國內線運作模式時，將黃金「合法」運入境。<br />\n<br />\n荷里活電影《巴利薛爾：飛常任務》中湯告魯斯飾演的巴利薛爾飛行技術超卓，表面上是民航機師，暗地裡走私違禁品。有一天他被中情局找上，要求協助收集情報，繼而運送違禁品，其後更結交毒販運毒，最終走上不歸路。"},{"pid":"f5d5ed495e89f03ae0b79b09c200b41120eeb7c5","tid":415446,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T03:55:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3afc15c422bf5d9785374296fb7c0c05c53db78a","tid":415446,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T03:55:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"664e45eb0445993a17d0c5178a68c7d4c4f64f40","tid":415446,"uid":70439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T03:56:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0687669d458a44bb048e7c47934c284bc7c936e8","tid":415446,"uid":47674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T03:56:23.000Z","msg":"香港航空<br />\n真係影衰晒香港個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1afda21114b29cb37dff78415651b003bd5a19bf","tid":415446,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T03:58:21.000Z","msg":"空少好專業架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d7383c9fae3aa5603faf436c5e4c5218f7d80f7","tid":415446,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T03:59:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>空少好專業架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n解款都識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca260ec18aa9f4997c8417742222a5407dbe7fa9","tid":415446,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T03:59:11.000Z","msg":"支那海南航空<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5925f249424b6cceccff92cef4f1e7ea98f4e4f","tid":415446,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T04:00:43.000Z","msg":"垃圾港畜又揚威國際<br />\n以後去大日本帝國又要俾人歧視<br />\n唉"},{"pid":"31d0edbd45bdab038d18bd426597b7ded8e5e4e3","tid":415446,"uid":52881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T04:02:34.000Z","msg":"廚叉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5c02de4ebc9374c777a7159cb91c56fa86cfa6d","tid":415446,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27